0.text: Innate: Cassiopeia cannot purchase boots and instead gains 4 − 72 (based on level)  bonus movement speed, for a total of 332 − 400 (based on level)  movement speed.

Active: Cassiopeia creates a blast at the target location which explodes after a 0.4-second delay. Enemies caught in the blast are  poisoned for 3 seconds, suffering magic damage every second over the duration.

1.text: Cassiopeia gains  bonus movement speed that decays over 3 seconds if Noxious Blast hits an enemy  champion.

0.text: Active: Cassiopeia spews forth eight bolts of venom in an arc at the target location, creating toxic clouds at the area for 5 seconds.

1.text: Enemies within the clouds are  poisoned to suffer magic damage every second,  grounded and  slowed by an amount that decays over the area's duration.

2.text: Miasma will cast at max range if cast beyond that.

0.text: Active: Cassiopeia launches her fangs at the target enemy that upon arrival deal them 52 − 120 (based on level) (+ 10% AP) magic damage. If Twin Fang kills the target, or the target is killed while in flight, the  mana cost is refunded.

1.text: Against a  poisoned target, Twin Fang deals bonus magic damage and  heals Cassiopeia. The heal is reduced by 75% against  minions and small  monsters.

0.text: Active: Cassiopeia blasts enemies in a cone in the target direction, dealing magic damage to enemies hit.

1.text: Enemies facing Cassiopeia are  stunned for 2 seconds upon being hit by Petrifying Gaze, and all other affected enemies are instead  slowed by 40% for the same duration.
